node.text: The LG CX 77 In OLED TV, The LG Styler, and also, the new LG washer and dryer that I surprised my parents with! Being able to stay connected to all of my appliances with the LG ThinQ app is so convenient! I can control them or track their progress on my phone or on the dashboard of my TV! As per my experience, increasing the number of appliances connected to LG ThinQ makes life simple and easier. Gotta love this smart technology with such a sleek design! #ad #lgoled #LGThinQ #ThinQ #SmartHome

node.title: Sharing some of my newest LG appliances with you!

node.text:
Love the new Washer & Dryer setup with LG ThinQ Technology. You can track any compatible appliances through the ThinQ App and on the Home Dashboard on my LG OLED TV. Being able to control everything from my phone has been a life saver, especially when I have conference calls or I’m busy with my kids! Convenience at its finest! Make your home smart with LG ThinQ and stay focused on what matters. 

#LGThinQ #ThinQ #SmartHome #Ad

node.text:
Check out my new LG Styler with ThinQ Technology! Perfect for sanitizing, reducing odors, steaming and removing wrinkles from our clothing. I can select the settings and run the styler at anytime and anywhere with LG ThinQ App on my phone easily. My husband and I thought this would be a great choice given our busy lifestyle. Love the mirror finish and how it seamlessly ties into any room. Convenience without sacrificing style. 
#LGThinQ #ThinQ #SmartHome #Ad

node.text:
Sharing with you my New LG CX 77 inch OLED TV with AI ThinQ Technology. Love the sleek design and how it fits seamlessly into the room. The ThinQ technology keeps me connected through an LG ThinQ app on my phone so I can easily control my LG ThinQ appliances with just a tap on my screen. Love that I can track the progress of my appliances on the dashboard on my TV as well! 
#LGThinQ #ThinQ #SmartHome #Ad
